Interface Edge

All Known Implementing Classes:
Edge.ResolvedEdge, Edge.UnresolvedEdge
public sealed interface Edge permits Edge.UnresolvedEdge, Edge.ResolvedEdge
An edge of the mapper graph. More formally, this represents the connection between two vertices u and v of the graph, referred to as from and into.
